data.description: Don't miss your opportunity to own this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, and 2 car garage located in the Towne Park Estates community. The home is an open floor plan. The home is located on an irregular lot that has a chainlink fence. The back porch is screen-in. You will be able to enjoy your nights and evening relaxing outside in privacy and with plenty of room for entertaining. The community pool is just a short walk down the sidewalk. Close to hospitals, shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. This picturesque property boasts a serene and peaceful atmosphere, perfect for those seeking a tranquil retreat from the hustle and bustle. The appliances were updated in 2021, the home features a spacious layout with well-appointed rooms designed to accommodate all of your living needs. Step inside and be greeted by a living area flooded with natural light. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances and ample cabinetry, making meal prep and entertaining a breeze. Fridge: Premium quality from Samsung - purchased 2021, Dishwasher: purchased 5/23. Retreat to the cozy bedrooms, complete with ample storage, where you can rest and recharge after a long day. The exterior of the home is equally as inviting, with a beautifully landscaped yard and a covered patio, perfect for enjoying the Florida weather all year round. The property is just a stone's throw away from all the amenities you could ever need. The tenant is currently paying $2100.00 per month for rent. The lease expires on May 17th, 2024. Make this charming home your own and start living the life you've always dreamed of. Schedule a viewing today and experience the beauty for yourself!
